name: One Eye of Color and the Other of Sand
description: There are tribes, tribes trying, tribes vying, tribes dying. Smoke signal washroom, crossed message relay, air fogged decay, cough and we slay, delay, dash and repay. The old blues breaking through the news. Look a new car door to smash, get in the whip, running back, quarter sack, tick tack rack underage lolly rook, just, just, take a look.
